{
  "texts": [
    "Xie et al. [26] use FAIR database to fine-tune LLMs and design a downstream task named SII which aims to extract hierarchical, domain specific material and device information, such as composition, structure, preparation conditions, etc., from unstructured scientific texts.",
    "Zheng et al. [27] used prompt engineering to guide ChatGPT in the automation of text mining of metal-organic framework (MOF) synthesis conditions from diverse formats and styles of the scientific literature.",
    "InstructMol [28] adopts Vicuna to multiple chemical tasks with task-specific fine-tuning.",
    "Meta FAIR researchers launched the Open Materials 2024 (OMat24) dataset and large pre-trained models focusing on structural and compositional diversity.",
    "OMat24 dataset [29] is one of the largest publicly available datasets in material fields."
  ]
}